#.vscode/

# Flutter/Dart/Pub related
**/doc/api/
**/ios/Flutter/.last_build_id
.dart_tool/
.flutter-plugins-dependencies
.pub-cache/
.pub/
/build/
/coverage/

# Symbolication related
app.*.symbols

# Obfuscation related
app.*.map.json

# Android Studio will place build artifacts here
/android/app/debug
/android/app/profile
/android/app/release

# Firebase
.firebase/
firebase-debug.log
firestore-debug.log
ui-debug.log
.runtimeconfig.json
# Service-account private keys — NEVER commit
*-service-account.json
serviceAccountKey.json
# Emulator persisted data
/emulator-data/

# NOTE: firebase_options.dart, google-services.json and GoogleService-Info.plist
# are intentionally NOT ignored. Google considers these safe to commit (they hold
# public app identifiers, not secrets); access is protected by Firestore Security
# Rules + App Check, and CI/builds need them. Add them here only if your org policy
# requires it.
